      "content": "Your desire for restlessness and closure reflects a deep sense of exhaustion rather than a lack of hope. While finishing a life story seems dignified to you, you are not the last character; many find peace by transitioning rather than stopping, often guided by grief counselors or community support. It is completely valid to feel stuck in \"bookend\" despair, but you deserve to explore these themes with someone who can help you find meaning outside your current professional chapter.",
